<br>
From 16 to about 18 or 19 I quad kited scythe beetles in NK.<br>
<br>
From 20-24 I tried quad kiting crag spiders in EW they break off when you hurt them, but you an finsish them off ratehr easily. At 22 or 23 exp gets worse so I would suggest heading to LOIO and getting a group until 24.<br>
<br>
At 24 you get pillar of fire and you can quad kite again. The have 2 4 spawns of goblisn in LOIO. The first is left of the sarnak fort if you are facing the fort, the other is down the cosastline in some ruins (not where people quad the bloodgills)<br>
Once again I did this full speed, so you will need Sow/tboots/jboots.<br>
<br>
